In this<span class="_ _0"></span> journal, we delve int<span class="_ _0"></span>o a specific <span class="_ _0"></span>project that seeks to <span class="_ _0"></span>explore and understand </div><div class="t m0 x1 h2 y7 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls1 ws2">some of the<span class="_ _0"></span>se cutting<span class="_ _0"></span>-edge techniques<span class="_ _0"></span>. This project, while multi<span class="_ _0"></span>face<span class="_ _0"></span>ted, is organized <span class="_ _0"></span>into three </div><div class="t m0 x1 h2 y8 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls1 ws2">distinct work <span class="_ _0"></span>packages, each with <span class="_ _0"></span>its unique <span class="_ _0"></span>focus and objectives.<span class="_ _0"></span> </div><div class="t m0 x1 h2 y9 ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls1 ws2">The <span class="ff1">first packag<span class="_ _0"></span>e</span> is dedicated <span class="_ _0"></span>to the technological asses<span class="_ _0"></span>sment at AMFI. Here<span class="_ _0"></span>, the goal is t<span class="_ _0"></span>o </div><div class="t m0 x1 h2 ya ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls1 ws2">evaluate and contrast<span class="_ _0"></span> the two available t<span class="_ _0"></span>echnologies to <span class="_ _0"></span>pinpoin<span class="_ _0"></span>t <span class="_ _0"></span>the optimal scan sett<span class="_ _0"></span>ings that </div><div class="t m0 x1 h2 yb ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls1 ws2">would yield the<span class="_ _0"></span> best results. This ph<span class="_ _0"></span>ase is crucial as it se<span class="_ _0"></span>ts the foundation for the <span class="_ _0"></span>subsequent </div><div class="t m0 x1 h2 yc ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls1 ws2">stages, ensuring <span class="_ _0"></span>that the data acquired is<span class="_ _0"></span> of the highest<span class="_ _0"></span> quality.<span class="_ _0"></span> </div><div class="t m0 x1 h2 yd ff2 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls1 ws2">Moving on, the <span class="_ _0"></span><span class="ff1">second package</span> <span class="_ _0"></span>delves into <span class="_ _0"></span>the world of re<span class="_ _0"></span>meshin<span class="_ _0"></span>g.
